WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.500
Meet Maya. She needs help finding care, but distance and time make the next step unclear.

00:05.500 --> 00:12.000
At a trusted SozoRock hub, she can speak naturally or tap. English and Spanish are available from the start.

00:12.000 --> 00:23.000
Maya says, “I need a provider who can help me manage my medication.” SozoRock listens, confirms what she means, and keeps the interaction non-clinical.

00:23.000 --> 00:31.000
The platform finds an access pathway in her county and checks that the provider is licensed for her state.

00:31.000 --> 00:39.000
With Maya’s consent, the connection is prepared through the provider’s existing platform. The provider remains responsible for care.

00:39.000 --> 00:45.000
One clear next step. In her language. Access where people live. SozoRock Health.
